The user enters the information, each student stores grade information in a vector
Add the student’s first name and last name
Add the assignments and their maximum points
Enter the grade for the assignment Optionally
The program asks if the user wants to add another assignment
The program asks if the user wants to add another student
A complete report is generated

Input:

Name of the student: Ricardo
Last name of the student: Mottet
Assignment name: Quiz
Max grade: 100
Grade of the student: 90

Output:

LastName,FirstName,Quiz
Mottet,Ricardo,90

